ygData.subject: Ykesha? Just say Yes-sha
ygData.msgSnippet: Our newest (and our only) Level 50 - Donna the Barbarian Warrior - gave a shout on guildsay just last knight: OMG!!  The Lord with a Sword!!! And she won it!
ygData.messageBody:
Our newest (and our only) Level 50 - Donna the Barbarian Warrior - gave a
shout on guildsay just last knight:

"OMG!! The Lord with a Sword!!!"

And she won it! WTG Donna!!! She is also the first female Barbarian Warrior
to make 50 on our server!

And then on the next spawn she goes:

"OMG!!! Not again!!!"

Yes, it spawned 2 times in a row. So, to whoever axed about Ykesha... yup
still dropping!

Sylly Songsynger
Bard of the 36th Song
<Spirit of the Moon>
somewhere on Innoruuk
